reviewText:
Okay first off i was hoping for it all to be in one Blu-ray disc case in one disc not two diffrent blu-ray releases in a thin carboard type packing

Salem Witch Trails:2 out of 5
This film is too long for a low budget film so i lost interest after the first 30min

Salvage:1 out of 5
This film was cheaply made with a mis placed soundtrack littered all through out the film

Mortuary:4 out of 5
This is the only one good out of this set
